# README Sync Rule

When updating CLI or runtime behavior in this project, also update [README.md](mdc:README.md) in the same change.

Scope includes changes to:
- `biostat_cli/cli.py`
- `biostat_cli/cli_parallel.py`
- `biostat_cli/config.py`
- `biostat_cli/evaluators/*`
- `biostat_cli/stats/*`

Update README sections affected by the change, especially CLI arguments, defaults/validation, output schemas, and examples.
